      <title>普里扬卡·甘地将在印度补选中首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/priyanka-gandhi-vadra-to-make-electoral-debut-to-retain-key-india-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼赫鲁-甘地政治王朝的后代普里扬卡·甘地·瓦德拉 (Priyanka Gandhi Vadra) 将在其兄长、反对党印度国民大会党高层领导人拉胡尔·甘地 (Rahul Gandhi) 最近赢得的选区首次参加选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/priyanka-gandhi-vadra-to-make-electoral-debut-to-retain-key-india-seat</guid>
