    <item>
      <title>英国医院财务状况不佳——而且没有一方有治疗方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-uk-nhs-trusts-funding-hospital-finances-debt/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[医疗保健是英国大选的关键议题，但两大政党均未提议对 NHS 紧张的财政状况进行彻底反思。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-uk-nhs-trusts-funding-hospital-finances-debt/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
