    <item>
      <title>朝鲜军队再次越过边界 朝方鸣枪警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/warning-shots-fired-as-north-korean-troops-cross-border-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数十名朝鲜士兵短暂跨越朝鲜半岛边界，韩国士兵向他们发射警告射击，这是不到两周内发生的第二起此类事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/warning-shots-fired-as-north-korean-troops-cross-border-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国医生将因争夺医学院席位而大规模罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/south-korean-doctors-set-for-mass-walkout-over-med-school-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最大的医生游说团体于周二呼吁全国范围内进行为期一天的罢工，加大对为期四个月的抗议政府增加医学院招生数量决定的劳工行动的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/south-korean-doctors-set-for-mass-walkout-over-med-school-seats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 01:46:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前总理他信因侮辱王室正式受到指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦于周二因涉嫌侮辱王室而受到正式指控，几个小时后，法庭将审议取消总理斯雷塔·塔维辛任职资格的申请——这两起备受关注的案件有可能让这个东南亚国家陷入政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的困境令欧洲担忧国防和乌克兰问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/macron-s-struggles-have-europe-fretting-over-defense-and-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的政治动荡引起一些欧盟国家政府的担忧，他们担心联合军费开支和新一轮支持乌克兰的举措可能会被搁置。]]></description>
